<darkcolour>A6416E</darkcolour><section><title>&lt;I&gt;So&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;neither&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>Use &lt;I&gt;so&lt;/I&gt; + the auxiliary (e.g. do, am, have, etc.) when you agree with (or have the same experience as) an affirmative statement.</sectiontitle><titlesound>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>I like apples.</text1><sound1>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;So do&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; I.</text1a><text2>I played the piano.</text2><sound2>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;So did&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; I.</text2a><titlesound2>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_4.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use the opposite auxiliary to say you disagree or have a different experience.</sectiontitle2><text3>I like bananas.</text3><sound3>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>I &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;don't.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text3a><text4>I am good at tennis.</text4><sound4>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;I'm not.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text4a></section><section><title>&lt;I&gt;So&lt;/I&gt; and &lt;I&gt;neither&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>Use &lt;I&gt;neither&lt;/I&gt; + the auxiliary (e.g. do, am, have, etc.) to agree with (or have the same experience as) a negative statement.</sectiontitle><titlesound>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_7.mp3</titlesound><text1>I don't like lemonade.</text1><sound1>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_8.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Neither do I.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text1a><text2>I wasn't here yesterday.</text2><sound2>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_9.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Neither was I.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text2a><titlesound2>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_10.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use the opposite auxiliary to say you disagree or have a different experience.</sectiontitle2><text3>I haven't seen the film.</text3><sound3>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_11.mp3</sound3><text3a>I &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;have.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text3a><text4>I didn't take any photos.</text4><sound4>Pre-intGRAM_2_2_12.mp3</sound4><text4a>I &lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;did.&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt;</text4a></section></grammar>